Great neighborhood spot! I ordered takeout but Oggi would be a wonderful place to go for a date, with the family, or just grab a drink and some food at the bar. I had the Arrabbiata pasta which was delicious! Hint of spicy heat was just right! Also had the Oggi Special Pizza and added giardeniera. In a pizza town, it was just ok. I ordered lunch via DoorDash today. I ordered the "Rigatoni Alla Vodka". I feel like I ordered from a different restaurant than the place people did who left amazing reviews. I received the pasta dish and was thoroughly disappointed with it. The lack of sauce for more than half of the pasta made a lot of the noodles dried out and unappetizing. I am in no way a food critic, but the pasta wasn't very flavorful even with a lot of it being dried out pasta.  I was really looking forward to my lunch as I finally found a local restaurant with amazing reviews. One of the last reviews mentioned the Tiramisu which I also ordered. I haven't had many pieces of tiramisu before but it was actually really good. I enjoyed it very much and would recommend it. If you told me both the tiramisu and the pasta were made in same restaurant, I wouldn't believe you.  I would like to give this place a second chance, and probably will do so in the future ordering something completely different. I'm hoping this was just a one-off and that other dishes are actually really good.

I LOVE THIS PLACE! Not only do they offer a wide variety of options from seafood to steak to chicken and the best pasta dishes around, you can get your entree prepared with any of their homemade sauces including (limone, cacciatore, vesuvio or velasco). Grilled and fried options are also offered for many dishes. I can’t decide if I prefer the fried calamari or the grilled octopus with its special sauce alongside some warm, soft freshly baked bread 🤤. I especially enjoy the welcoming atmosphere there. It’s a great place for a date, for hanging out at the bar sharing one of their delicious pizzas over drinks from the full bar complete with top shelf liquor options, beer and a very nice wine selection. Families are welcomed too. I’ve entertained many friends, family, business lunch meetings as well as attended a private party with a selection of some of their customer favorites on the menu. This family owned restaurant will make you feel at home in an elegant yet comfortable setting with very friendly staff all while listening to the nice mix of soft music playing in the background or watching the game on the big screen at the bar. Oggi Trattoria is top notch when it comes to some great Italian cuisine.
